{
  "video_id": "eVFYhbHpfqU",
  "title": "A smog vacuum cleaner and other magical city designs | Daan Roosegaarde",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12423.0,
      "end_time": 14972.0,
      "text": "Do you remember these glow-in-the-dark little stars"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14997.0,
      "end_time": 17887.0,
      "text": "which you had on the ceiling when you were a boy or a girl?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17911.0,
      "end_time": 19121.0,
      "text": "Yes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19145.0,
      "end_time": 20341.0,
      "text": "It is light."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20365.0,
      "end_time": 21549.0,
      "text": "It is pure light."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 21573.0,
      "end_time": 23475.0,
      "text": "I think I stared at them way too long"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 23499.0,
      "end_time": 25272.0,
      "text": "when I was a five-year-old, you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25296.0,
      "end_time": 26520.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s so beautiful:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26544.0,
      "end_time": 29301.0,
      "text": "no energy bill, no maintenance."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 29325.0,
      "end_time": 30529.0,
      "text": "It is there."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30553.0,
      "end_time": 32610.0,
      "text": "So two years ago, we went back to the lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32634.0,
      "end_time": 34932.0,
      "text": "making it more durable, more light-emitting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34956.0,
      "end_time": 36336.0,
      "text": "with the experts."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 36360.0,
      "end_time": 40410.0,
      "text": "And at the same time, we got a request from this guy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40650.0,
      "end_time": 42643.0,
      "text": "Van Gogh, the famous Van Gogh Foundation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42667.0,
      "end_time": 46643.0,
      "text": "who wanted to celebrate his 125th anniversary in the Netherlands."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 47520.0,
      "end_time": 48917.0,
      "text": "And they came to me and asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48941.0,
      "end_time": 52742.0,
      "text": "\"Can you make a place where he feels more alive again"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 52766.0,
      "end_time": 53972.0,
      "text": "in the Netherlands?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 53996.0,
      "end_time": 55550.0,
      "text": "And I liked that question a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 55574.0,
      "end_time": 56727.0,
      "text": "so in way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 56752.0,
      "end_time": 59801.0,
      "text": "we sort of started to connect these two different worlds."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 60847.0,
      "end_time": 62144.0,
      "text": "This is how my brain works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 62168.0,
      "end_time": 63318.0,
      "text": "by the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 63342.0,
      "end_time": 64393.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 64417.0,
      "end_time": 66628.0,
      "text": "I would love to keep on doing this for an hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 66652.0,
      "end_time": 67803.0,
      "text": "but OK --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 67827.0,
      "end_time": 68835.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 68859.0,
      "end_time": 70637.0,
      "text": "And this is the result that we made:"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 70661.0,
      "end_time": 73383.0,
      "text": "a bicycle path which charges at daytime via the sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 73407.0,
      "end_time": 75529.0,
      "text": "and glows at night, up to eight hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 75553.0,
      "end_time": 76780.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 76805.0,
      "end_time": 78131.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 78155.0,
      "end_time": 82522.0,
      "text": "... hinting towards a future which should be energy friendly"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 82546.0,
      "end_time": 84242.0,
      "text": "and linking up the local grounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 84266.0,
      "end_time": 87693.0,
      "text": "as Van Gogh literally walked and lived there in 1883."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 87717.0,
      "end_time": 91240.0,
      "text": "And you can go there every night for free, no ticket needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 91480.0,
      "end_time": 94254.0,
      "text": "People experience the beauty of cycling through the starry night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 94278.0,
      "end_time": 96303.0,
      "text": "thinking about green energy and safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 96327.0,
      "end_time": 100420.0,
      "text": "I want to create places where people feel connected again."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 100586.0,
      "end_time": 103673.0,
      "text": "And it was somehow great to make these projects happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 103698.0,
      "end_time": 106544.0,
      "text": "with the industry, with the infrastructure companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 106568.0,
      "end_time": 108857.0,
      "text": "So when these sheikhs of Qatar started to call:"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 108881.0,
      "end_time": 110382.0,
      "text": "\"How much for 10 kilometers?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 110406.0,
      "end_time": 111421.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 111445.0,
      "end_time": 114157.0,
      "text": "Yeah, really, that&#39;s a weird call you&#39;re going to get."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 114181.0,
      "end_time": 115341.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s fascinating"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 115365.0,
      "end_time": 118773.0,
      "text": "that this is not just a sort of one-off, nice-to-have special."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 118797.0,
      "end_time": 122220.0,
      "text": "I think this kind of creative thinking, these kinds of connections --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 122244.0,
      "end_time": 123428.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the new economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 123452.0,
      "end_time": 126199.0,
      "text": "The World Economic Forum, the think tank in Geneva,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 126223.0,
      "end_time": 128621.0,
      "text": "did an interview with a lot of smart people"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 128645.00000000001,
      "end_time": 129801.00000000001,
      "text": "all around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 129826.0,
      "end_time": 134648.0,
      "text": "asking, \"What are the top 10 skills you and I need to become successful?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 134672.0,
      "end_time": 136992.0,
      "text": "And what is interesting, what you see here:"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 137160.0,
      "end_time": 139554.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not about money"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 139579.0,
      "end_time": 142480.0,
      "text": "or being really good in C++,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 142504.0,
      "end_time": 145521.0,
      "text": "although these are great skills to have, I have to admit."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 145545.0,
      "end_time": 147900.0,
      "text": "But look at number three, creativity;"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 147925.0,
      "end_time": 150137.0,
      "text": "number two, critical thinking;"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 150161.0,
      "end_time": 153261.0,
      "text": "number one, complex problem-solving --"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 153285.0,
      "end_time": 157805.0,
      "text": "all the things a robot or a computer is really bad at."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 158482.0,
      "end_time": 162135.0,
      "text": "And this makes me very optimistic, very hopeful for the new world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 162159.0,
      "end_time": 165350.0,
      "text": "that as we will live in this hyper-technological world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 165590.0,
      "end_time": 166501.0,
      "text": "our human skills --"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 166525.0,
      "end_time": 167869.0,
      "text": "our desire for empathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167893.0,
      "end_time": 170159.0,
      "text": "our desire for curiosity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 170183.0,
      "end_time": 171898.0,
      "text": "our desire for beauty --"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 171922.0,
      "end_time": 173656.0,
      "text": "will be more appreciated again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 173680.0,
      "end_time": 177496.0,
      "text": "and we will live in a world where creativity is our true capital."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 178604.0,
      "end_time": 181630.0,
      "text": "And a creative process like that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 181870.0,
      "end_time": 182786.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know how it works for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 182810.0,
      "end_time": 185501.0,
      "text": "but in my brain, it always starts with a question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 185525.0,
      "end_time": 186679.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 187704.0,
      "end_time": 190227.0,
      "text": "Why does a jellyfish emit light?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 190251.0,
      "end_time": 191606.0,
      "text": "Or a firefly?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 191630.0,
      "end_time": 193876.0,
      "text": "Or why do be accept pollution?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 193900.0,
      "end_time": 196149.0,
      "text": "This is from my room in Beijing three years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 196173.0,
      "end_time": 198317.0,
      "text": "Left image is a good day -- Saturday."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 198341.0,
      "end_time": 200562.0,
      "text": "I can see the cars and the people, the birds;"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 200586.0,
      "end_time": 203178.0,
      "text": "life is OK in a dense urban city."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 203202.0,
      "end_time": 205340.0,
      "text": "And on the right image --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 205580.0,
      "end_time": 206858.0,
      "text": "holy moly."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 206882.0,
      "end_time": 208895.0,
      "text": "Pollution -- complete layers."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 208919.0,
      "end_time": 211627.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t even see the other side of the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 211651.0,
      "end_time": 213487.0,
      "text": "And this image made me really sad."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 213511.0,
      "end_time": 216560.0,
      "text": "This is not the bright future we envision here at TED --"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 216584.0,
      "end_time": 217757.0,
      "text": "this is the horror."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 217781.0,
      "end_time": 219532.0,
      "text": "We live five to six years shorter;"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 219556.0,
      "end_time": 222245.0,
      "text": "children have lung cancer when they&#39;re six years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 222648.0,
      "end_time": 225134.0,
      "text": "And so in a weird, beautiful way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 225158.0,
      "end_time": 229311.0,
      "text": "I, at that moment, became inspired by Beijing smog."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 229669.0,
      "end_time": 233152.0,
      "text": "And the governments all around the world are fighting their war on smog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 233176.0,
      "end_time": 235814.0,
      "text": "but I wanted to make something within the now."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 235838.0,
      "end_time": 239636.0,
      "text": "So we decided to build the largest smog vacuum cleaner"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 239660.0,
      "end_time": 241710.0,
      "text": "in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 241950.0,
      "end_time": 243440.0,
      "text": "It sucks up polluted air, cleans it"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 243680.0,
      "end_time": 244492.0,
      "text": "and then releases it."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 244516.0,
      "end_time": 246206.0,
      "text": "And we built the first one."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 246685.0,
      "end_time": 249322.0,
      "text": "So it sucks up 30,000 cubic meters per hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 249346.0,
      "end_time": 253133.0,
      "text": "cleans it on the nano level -- the PM2.5, PM10 particles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 253157.0,
      "end_time": 255132.0,
      "text": "using very little electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 255156.0,
      "end_time": 257623.0,
      "text": "and then releases the clean air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 257647.0,
      "end_time": 263990.0,
      "text": "so we have parks, playgrounds, which are 55 to 75 percent more clean"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 263124.0,
      "end_time": 264691.0,
      "text": "than the rest of the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 264715.0,
      "end_time": 266383.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 266408.0,
      "end_time": 267836.0,
      "text": "Yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 267860.0,
      "end_time": 269377.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 269401.0,
      "end_time": 272298.0,
      "text": "And every month or so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 272322.0,
      "end_time": 276213.0,
      "text": "it opens like a spaceship --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 276237.0,
      "end_time": 278896.0,
      "text": "like a Marilyn Monroe with the -- well, you know what."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 278920.0,
      "end_time": 280110.0,
      "text": "Anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 280134.0,
      "end_time": 281210.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 281234.0,
      "end_time": 282683.0,
      "text": "So this ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 282708.0,
      "end_time": 284655.0,
      "text": "this is the stuff we are capturing."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 285130.0,
      "end_time": 286877.0,
      "text": "This is Beijing smog."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 287580.0,
      "end_time": 289198.0,
      "text": "This is in our lungs right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 289222.0,
      "end_time": 292644.0,
      "text": "If you live next to a highway, it&#39;s the same as 17 cigarettes per day."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 292668.0,
      "end_time": 293818.0,
      "text": "Are we insane?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 293842.0,
      "end_time": 295425.0,
      "text": "When did we say yes to that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 295848.0,
      "end_time": 299910.0,
      "text": "And we had buckets of this disgusting material"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 299115.0,
      "end_time": 300659.0,
      "text": "in our studio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 300683.0,
      "end_time": 303492.0,
      "text": "and on a Monday morning, we were discussing, we were like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 303516.0,
      "end_time": 306366.0,
      "text": "\"Shit, what should we do with it? Should we throw it away?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 306390.0,
      "end_time": 307544.0,
      "text": "Like, \"Help!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 307569.0,
      "end_time": 309730.0,
      "text": "And then we realized: no, no, no, no, no --"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 309754.0,
      "end_time": 310946.0,
      "text": "waste should not exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 310970.0,
      "end_time": 313398.0,
      "text": "Waste for the one should be food for the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 314170.0,
      "end_time": 316322.0,
      "text": "So, here, maybe show it around."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 316690.0,
      "end_time": 318253.0,
      "text": "Do not put this in your coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 318277.0,
      "end_time": 319288.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 319312.0,
      "end_time": 322323.0,
      "text": "And we realized that 42 percent is made out of carbon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 322347.0,
      "end_time": 324515.0,
      "text": "and carbon, of course, under high pressure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 324539.0,
      "end_time": 325810.0,
      "text": "you get ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 326691.0,
      "end_time": 328940.0,
      "text": "diamonds."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 328119.0,
      "end_time": 332250.0,
      "text": "So, inspired by that, we compress it for 30 minutes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 332274.0,
      "end_time": 333361.0,
      "text": "(Cracking sound)"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 333385.0,
      "end_time": 335465.0,
      "text": "and make smog-free rings."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 335489.0,
      "end_time": 336512.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 336536.0,
      "end_time": 338512.0,
      "text": "And so by sharing -- yeah, really!"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 338536.0,
      "end_time": 340174.0,
      "text": "And so by sharing a ring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 340198.0,
      "end_time": 342804.0,
      "text": "you donate 1,000 cubic meters of clean air"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 342828.0,
      "end_time": 344493.0,
      "text": "to the city the tower is in."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 344517.0,
      "end_time": 345529.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 345553.0,
      "end_time": 346783.0,
      "text": "I have one here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 346807.0,
      "end_time": 347987.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 348110.0,
      "end_time": 350878.0,
      "text": "A little floating cube."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 351983.0,
      "end_time": 353133.0,
      "text": "I will give one to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 353157.0,
      "end_time": 355387.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to propose, don&#39;t worry."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 355411.0,
      "end_time": 356699.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 356723.0,
      "end_time": 357888.0,
      "text": "Are we good?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 357912.0,
      "end_time": 359154.0,
      "text": "You can show it around."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 359178.0,
      "end_time": 362588.0,
      "text": "And we put this online -- Kickstarter campaign, crowdfunding."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 362612.0,
      "end_time": 364401.0,
      "text": "And people started to preorder it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 364425.0,
      "end_time": 367255.0,
      "text": "but more importantly, they started to prepay it."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 367279.0,
      "end_time": 370648.0,
      "text": "So the finance we made with the jewelry helped us to realize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 370672.0,
      "end_time": 372297.0,
      "text": "to build the first tower."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 372693.0,
      "end_time": 373842.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 373867.0,
      "end_time": 376504.0,
      "text": "So the waste the activator, it was the enabler."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 376528.0,
      "end_time": 378538.0,
      "text": "Also, the feedback from the community --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 378562.0,
      "end_time": 380378.0,
      "text": "this is a wedding couple from India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 380402.0,
      "end_time": 382863.0,
      "text": "where he proposed to her with the smog-free ring"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 382887.0,
      "end_time": 384160.0,
      "text": "as a sign of true beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 384184.0,
      "end_time": 386530.0,
      "text": "as a sign of hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 386770.0,
      "end_time": 387915.0,
      "text": "And she said yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 387939.0,
      "end_time": 389654.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 389678.0,
      "end_time": 393161.0,
      "text": "I love this image so much for a lot of different reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 393185.0,
      "end_time": 394412.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 394436.0,
      "end_time": 397131.0,
      "text": "And right now, the project is touring through China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 397155.0,
      "end_time": 400270.0,
      "text": "actually with the support of China&#39;s central government."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 400510.0,
      "end_time": 403144.0,
      "text": "So the first goal is to create local clean-air parks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 403168.0,
      "end_time": 405168.0,
      "text": "and that works already quite well --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 405192.0,
      "end_time": 407452.0,
      "text": "55, 75 percent more clean."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 407476.0,
      "end_time": 408825.0,
      "text": "And at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 408849.0,
      "end_time": 410246.0,
      "text": "we team up with the NGOs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 410270.0,
      "end_time": 411433.0,
      "text": "with the governors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 411458.0,
      "end_time": 412658.0,
      "text": "with the students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 412682.0,
      "end_time": 413833.0,
      "text": "with the tech people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 413857.0,
      "end_time": 417212.0,
      "text": "to say, \"Hey, what do we need to do to make a whole city smog-free?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 417236.0,
      "end_time": 419190.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about the dream of clean air."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 419430.0,
      "end_time": 421289.0,
      "text": "We do workshops. New ideas pop up."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 421313.0,
      "end_time": 424107.0,
      "text": "These are smog-free bicycles which -- I&#39;m Dutch, yes? --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 424131.0,
      "end_time": 426570.0,
      "text": "I have this \"bicycle DNA\" inside of me somewhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 426594.0,
      "end_time": 428244.0,
      "text": "And so it sucks up polluted air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 428268.0,
      "end_time": 429827.0,
      "text": "it cleans it and releases it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 429851.0,
      "end_time": 431344.0,
      "text": "in the fight against the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 431368.0,
      "end_time": 433248.0,
      "text": "in the celebration of the bicycle."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 433273.0,
      "end_time": 437434.0,
      "text": "And so right now, we&#39;re working on a sort of \"package deal,\" so to speak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 437458.0,
      "end_time": 440712.0,
      "text": "where we say, \"Smog-free towers, smog-free rings.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 440736.0,
      "end_time": 443232.0,
      "text": "We go to the mayors or the governors of this world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 443256.0,
      "end_time": 447359.0,
      "text": "and say, \"We can guarantee a short-term reduction of pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 447383.0,
      "end_time": 449466.0,
      "text": "between 20 and 40 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 449490.0,
      "end_time": 451387.0,
      "text": "Please sign here right now.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 451411.0,
      "end_time": 452562.0,
      "text": "Yes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 452586.0,
      "end_time": 454313.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 454337.0,
      "end_time": 455486.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 455511.0,
      "end_time": 457341.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 457365.0,
      "end_time": 462292.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s all about connecting new technology with creative thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 462316.0,
      "end_time": 464258.0,
      "text": "And if you start thinking about that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 464282.0,
      "end_time": 466443.0,
      "text": "there is so much you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 466467.0,
      "end_time": 467990.0,
      "text": "so much more you can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 468140.0,
      "end_time": 471325.0,
      "text": "We worked on dance floors which produce electricity"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 471349.0,
      "end_time": 472608.0,
      "text": "when you dance on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 472632.0,
      "end_time": 475110.0,
      "text": "We did the design for that -- 2008."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 475134.0,
      "end_time": 477129.0,
      "text": "So it moves eight or nine millimeters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 477153.0,
      "end_time": 478831.0,
      "text": "produces 25 watts."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 478855.0,
      "end_time": 482852.0,
      "text": "The electricity that we generate is used for the lighting or the DJ booth."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 482876.0,
      "end_time": 485539.0,
      "text": "So some of the sustainability is about doing more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 485564.0,
      "end_time": 487227.0,
      "text": "not about doing less."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 487251.0,
      "end_time": 488736.0,
      "text": "But also on a larger scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 488761.0,
      "end_time": 492210.0,
      "text": "the Netherlands, where I&#39;m from, we live below sea level."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 492234.0,
      "end_time": 494512.0,
      "text": "So because of these beauties --"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 494536.0,
      "end_time": 499976.0,
      "text": "the Afsluitdijk: 32 kilometers, built by hand in 1932 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 500000.0,
      "end_time": 501767.0,
      "text": "we live with the water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 501791.0,
      "end_time": 503320.0,
      "text": "we fight with the water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 503345.0,
      "end_time": 505491.0,
      "text": "we try to find harmony,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 505515.0,
      "end_time": 507416.0,
      "text": "but sometimes we forget."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 507983.0,
      "end_time": 509926.0,
      "text": "And therefore, we made \"Waterlicht,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 509950.0,
      "end_time": 512169.0,
      "text": "a combination of LEDs and lenses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 512193.0,
      "end_time": 514808.0,
      "text": "which show how high the water level would be --"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 514832.0,
      "end_time": 516112.0,
      "text": "global change --"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 516679.0,
      "end_time": 518203.0,
      "text": "if we stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 518227.0,
      "end_time": 520929.0,
      "text": "If, today, we all go home and we say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 520953.0,
      "end_time": 523374.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, whatever, somebody else will do it for us,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 523398.0,
      "end_time": 525418.0,
      "text": "or we&#39;ll wait for government or whomever."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 525442.0,
      "end_time": 527308.0,
      "text": "You know, we&#39;re not going to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 527332.0,
      "end_time": 528491.0,
      "text": "It goes wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 528515.0,
      "end_time": 531231.0,
      "text": "And we placed this in public spaces all around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 531255.0,
      "end_time": 532846.0,
      "text": "Thousands of people showed up."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 532870.0,
      "end_time": 534118.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 534142.0,
      "end_time": 535292.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 535937.0,
      "end_time": 539498.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re too nice, you&#39;re too nice. That&#39;s not good for a designer."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 539522.0,
      "end_time": 541522.0,
      "text": "So thousands of people showed up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 541546.0,
      "end_time": 543316.0,
      "text": "and some, actually, were scared."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 543340.0,
      "end_time": 546681.0,
      "text": "And they left; they experienced the floods in 1953."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 546705.0,
      "end_time": 548970.0,
      "text": "And others were mesmerized."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 548121.0,
      "end_time": 549939.0,
      "text": "Can we make floating cities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 549964.0,
      "end_time": 553451.0,
      "text": "Can we generate electricity from the change in tides?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 553864.0,
      "end_time": 556815.0,
      "text": "So I think it&#39;s so important to make experiences --"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 556839.0,
      "end_time": 558373.0,
      "text": "collective experiences --"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 558397.0,
      "end_time": 562510.0,
      "text": "where people feel connected with a vision, with a future"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 562750.0,
      "end_time": 563845.0,
      "text": "and trigger what is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 564642.0,
      "end_time": 566120.0,
      "text": "At the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 566360.0,
      "end_time": 570530.0,
      "text": "you know, these kinds of things -- they&#39;re not easy, yes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 570554.0,
      "end_time": 571808.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a struggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 571832.0,
      "end_time": 573498.0,
      "text": "And what I experienced in my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 573522.0,
      "end_time": 575921.0,
      "text": "is that a lot of people say they want innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 575945.0,
      "end_time": 578543.0,
      "text": "and they want the next and the new, the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 578567.0,
      "end_time": 581604.0,
      "text": "But the moment you present a new idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 581628.0,
      "end_time": 586140.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s this weird tendency to reply to every new idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 586380.0,
      "end_time": 588392.0,
      "text": "starting with two words."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 589288.0,
      "end_time": 590470.0,
      "text": "Which are?"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 590494.0,
      "end_time": 591840.0,
      "text": "(Audience guesses)"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 591864.0,
      "end_time": 594460.0,
      "text": "No, not \"How much?\" It&#39;s more annoying."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 594700.0,
      "end_time": 595780.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 595102.0,
      "end_time": 596255.0,
      "text": "What is it, guys?"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 596279.0,
      "end_time": 598820.0,
      "text": "Or you&#39;re really blessed people? That&#39;s really good."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 598844.0,
      "end_time": 600400.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, but.\" Very good."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 600640.0,
      "end_time": 603756.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, but: it&#39;s too expensive, it&#39;s too cheap, it&#39;s too fast, it&#39;s too slow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 603780.0,
      "end_time": 607262.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s too beautiful, it&#39;s too ugly, it cannot be done, it already exists.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 607287.0,
      "end_time": 609374.0,
      "text": "I heard everything about the same project"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 609398.0,
      "end_time": 610558.0,
      "text": "in the same week."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 610582.0,
      "end_time": 612511.0,
      "text": "And I got really, really annoyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 612535.0,
      "end_time": 616773.0,
      "text": "I got a bit of gray hair, started to dress in black like a true architect."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 616797.0,
      "end_time": 619245.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 619269.0,
      "end_time": 622727.0,
      "text": "And one morning I woke up and I said, \"Daan, stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 622751.0,
      "end_time": 624102.0,
      "text": "This is dragging you down."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 624126.0,
      "end_time": 625881.0,
      "text": "You have to do something with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 625905.0,
      "end_time": 628600.0,
      "text": "You have to use it as an ingredient, as a component.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 628624.0,
      "end_time": 630589.0,
      "text": "And so we decided to build,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 630613.0,
      "end_time": 634596.0,
      "text": "to realize the famous \"Yes, but\" chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 634620.0,
      "end_time": 638257.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 638281.0,
      "end_time": 641635.0,
      "text": "And this is an existing chair by Friso Kramer, a Dutch design."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 641659.0,
      "end_time": 644443.0,
      "text": "But we gave it a little \"update,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 644467.0,
      "end_time": 646798.0,
      "text": "a little \"hack,\" so to speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 646822.0,
      "end_time": 650116.0,
      "text": "We placed a little voice-recognition element right here."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 650920.0,
      "end_time": 653717.0,
      "text": "So the moment you sit on that chair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 653741.0,
      "end_time": 657260.0,
      "text": "and you say those two horrible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 657510.0,
      "end_time": 661501.0,
      "text": "creative-destructive, annoying little words --"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 661525.0,
      "end_time": 662616.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 662640.0,
      "end_time": 664295.0,
      "text": "you get a short --"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 664319.0,
      "end_time": 665942.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 665966.0,
      "end_time": 667539.0,
      "text": "but pretty intense"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 667563.0,
      "end_time": 670378.0,
      "text": "little shock on the back side of your bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 670402.0,
      "end_time": 671559.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 671583.0,
      "end_time": 672972.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 672996.0,
      "end_time": 674167.0,
      "text": "And --"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 674191.0,
      "end_time": 675219.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 675243.0,
      "end_time": 677410.0,
      "text": "and that works; yeah, that works."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 677650.0,
      "end_time": 679840.0,
      "text": "Some clients have left us, they got really mad."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 679864.0,
      "end_time": 681845.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, the good ones have stayed."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 681869.0,
      "end_time": 684256.0,
      "text": "And, of course, we also apply it to ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 684280.0,
      "end_time": 687425.0,
      "text": "But ladies and gentlemen, let&#39;s not be afraid."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 687450.0,
      "end_time": 689221.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s be curious, yes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 689245.0,
      "end_time": 691763.0,
      "text": "And, you know, walking through TED in these days"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 691787.0,
      "end_time": 693486.0,
      "text": "and hearing the other speakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 693510.0,
      "end_time": 695930.0,
      "text": "and feeling the energy of the crowd,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 695954.0,
      "end_time": 700252.0,
      "text": "I was remembering this quote of the Canadian author, Marshall McLuhan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 700277.0,
      "end_time": 702292.0,
      "text": "who once famously said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 702316.0,
      "end_time": 704195.0,
      "text": "\"On spacecraft earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 704219.0,
      "end_time": 705735.0,
      "text": "there are no passengers."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 705759.0,
      "end_time": 708307.0,
      "text": "We are all crew.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 708846.0,
      "end_time": 711640.0,
      "text": "And I think this so beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 711880.0,
      "end_time": 712540.0,
      "text": "This is so beautiful!"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 712564.0,
      "end_time": 714810.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not just consumers; we&#39;re makers:"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 714834.0,
      "end_time": 716400.0,
      "text": "we make decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 716640.0,
      "end_time": 717235.0,
      "text": "we make new inventions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 717259.0,
      "end_time": 718489.0,
      "text": "we make new dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 718896.0,
      "end_time": 720560.0,
      "text": "And I think"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 720810.0,
      "end_time": 724146.0,
      "text": "if we start implementing that kind of thinking even more"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 724170.0,
      "end_time": 725712.0,
      "text": "within today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 726371.0,
      "end_time": 729190.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s still a whole new world to be explored."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 730365.0,
      "end_time": 731799.0,
      "text": "All right, thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 731823.0,
      "end_time": 733951.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 733975.0,
      "end_time": 735125.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 735149.0,
      "end_time": 737149.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}